These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
There 4 different types of food: plum, cranberry, peach, artichoke
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, country, folk, trance
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, argentine, british, colombian
4 different pets are kept: dog, cat, bird, goat
 1. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of country##1
 2. the person eating plum is in an even position##4
 3. the malaysian is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 4. the british is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
 5. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
 6. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
 7. the argentine is the person eating peach##1
 8. the owner of the bird is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the dog is between the owner of the goat and the fan of trance##2
10. the person eating plum is the owner of the goat##1
11. the fan of folk is the person eating artichoke##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | peach  | plum    | artichoke    | cranberry   |
| Music-Genre   | country     | soul   | folk       | trance    |
| Nationality   | argentine | malaysian | colombian    | british |
| Pet           | cat | goat       | dog | bird     |

