.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, orange, corn, lemon
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, camping, cooking, board-games
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, french, german, japanese
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, swimming, water-polo, golf
 1. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an even position##4
 2. the french is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person eating corn##1
 4. the person eating orange is the thai##1
 5. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
 6. the thai is on the left or right of the german##3
 7. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person eating corn##1
 8. the japanese is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
 9. the german is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating corn is in an odd position##4
11. the german is the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Food          | kiwi  | orange    | corn     | lemon       |
| Hobby         | cooking | board-games | puzzles   | camping |
| Nationality   | german | thai   | french   | japanese    |
| Sport         | water-polo | golf  | sailing | swimming   |

