.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, soy-milk, 7up, coffee
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, architect, pilot, electrician
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, malaysian, mexican, dutch
4 different pets are kept: turtle, guinea-pig, frog, pony
 1. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
 2. the malaysian is the pilot##1
 3. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
 4. the entrepreneur is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is the electrician##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 7. the owner of the turtle is the dutch##1
 8. the electrician is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the pakistani##1
10. the owner of the turtle is the person drinking 7up##1
11. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | fanta | 7up   | coffee    | soy-milk      |
| Job           | pilot | entrepreneur | architect | electrician     |
| Nationality   | malaysian      | dutch   | pakistani   | mexican |
| Pet           | pony         | turtle       | frog  | guinea-pig       |

