.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, 7up, soy-milk, cola
There 4 different types of food: avocado, grapes, grapefruit, spinach
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, filmmaking, cooking, puzzles
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, soccer, snowboarding, sailing
 1. the person drinking coffee is the person eating avocado##1
 2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 3. the person eating avocado is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
 4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an even position##4
 5. the person drinking 7up is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 8. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the person eating spinach##3
 9. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
10. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
11. the person drinking soy-milk is the person eating spinach##1
12. the person eating spinach is on the left or right of the person eating avocado##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | cola       | soy-milk   | coffee   | 7up   |
| Food       | grapes        | spinach | avocado    | grapefruit       |
| Hobby      | puzzles | filmmaking    | cooking  | rock-climbing |
| Sport      | soccer  | snowboarding  | tennis | sailing    |

