.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, artichoke, nectarine, zucchini
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, skydiving, dancing, reading
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, videographer, electrician, freelancer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, baseball, sailing, cycling
 1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person eating zucchini##2
 3. the electrician is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 4. the videographer is the person eating watermelon##1
 5. the nurse is on the left or right of the videographer##3
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an even position##4
 7. the person eating artichoke is the nurse##1
 8. the person who's hobby is dancing is the videographer##1
 9. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
10. the videographer is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
11. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person eating nectarine##3
12. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Food    | nectarine    | zucchini      | watermelon          | artichoke    |
| Hobby   | skydiving | reading       | dancing | filmmaking |
| Job     | freelancer     | electrician      | videographer     | nurse |
| Sport   | baseball   | cycling | sailing        | tennis   |

