 2. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 3. the person eating corn is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 5. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan of jazz is between the turkish and the fan of indie##2
 7. the fan of salsa is the person eating pineapple##1
 8. the person drinking milk is the person eating pineapple##1
 9. the argentine is on the far right##1
10. the italian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk  | milk    | juice       | coffee       |
| Food          | onion    | pineapple | apricot | corn     |
| Music-Genre   | techno | salsa        | jazz    | indie   |
| Nationality   | italian  | turkish      | japanese    | argentine |

