There are 4 different nationalities: indian, argentine, colombian, thai
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, rabbit, snake, hedgehog
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, motorbike, boat, train
 1. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 2. the thai is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 3. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
 4. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the indian##3
 5. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 6. the colombian is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 7. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
 8. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
 9. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
10. the argentine is on the far right##1
11. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
12. the owner of the chinchilla is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | time-travel    | comedy  | musical      |
| Nationality   | indian      | colombian | thai | argentine   |
| Pet           | snake       | hedgehog | chinchilla   | rabbit       |
| Transport     | train      | boat | bike  | motorbike |

