There are 4 different nationalities: french, italian, indonesian, malaysian
4 different pets are kept: mouse, pony, goldfish, fish
 1. the owner of the fish is in an odd position##4
 2. the owner of the mouse is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the goldfish##2
 3. the french is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 4. the person watching family movies is in an odd position##4
 5. the malaysian is on the right of the indonesian##1
 6. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
 7. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 8. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the italian##1
 9. the owner of the mouse is between the french and the person watching scientific movies##2
10. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
11. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an even position##4
12. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Hobby         | sudoku  | magic-tricks    | card-games    | fishing |
