.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, cauliflower, broccoli, avocado
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, thriller, mystery, scientific
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, electronic, d&b, salsa
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, weightlifting, climbing
 1. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
 2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4
 3. the fan of punk is between the person watching thriller movies and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
 4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
 5. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
 6. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
 7. the fan of salsa is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's sport is climbing is the person watching thriller movies##1
 9. the person eating zucchini is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
11. the person eating zucchini is on the far left or far right##3
12. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
13. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person eating avocado##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |      4       |
| Food          | zucchini     | broccoli      | avocado  | cauliflower        |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller     | mystery | superhero | scientific      |
| Music-Genre   | electronic      | punk        | salsa        | d&b        |
| Sport         | climbing | cricket    | ice-hockey      | weightlifting |

