The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, manager, bartender, librarian
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, german, thai, egyptian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, baseball, cycling, water-polo
 1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
 2. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 3. the manager is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person who's sport is cricket##2
 4. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the egyptian##1
 5. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the thai is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far right##1
 8. the egyptian is on the right of the thai##1
 9. the librarian is on the left of the manager##1
10. the photographer is in an even position##4
11. the indonesian is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |       3        |       4       |
| Beverage      | coffee      | 7up      | iced-tea           | almond-milk |
| Job           | librarian | manager | bartender | photographer        |
| Nationality   | thai      | egyptian  | indonesian          | german      |
| Sport         | water-polo       | cycling    | cricket       | baseball       |

