.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, cola, water, soy-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, gardening, fishing, camping
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, superhero, horror, family
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, cricket, handball
 1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 2. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 3. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 4. the person watching superhero movies is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 7. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
10. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
11. the person watching family movies is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | water       | cola | fanta        | soy-milk        |
| Hobby         | camping | fishing       | cooking | gardening |
| Movie-Genre   | family     | superhero        | documentary    | horror      |
| Sport         | basketball     | cricket    | handball | baseball   |

