.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, metal, country, soul
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, mexican, brazilian, spanish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, basketball, surfing, ice-hockey
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, boat, tram, bus
 1. the fan of soul is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 2. the person who's sport is surfing is between the russian and the spanish##2
 3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
 4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the mexican##1
 5. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 6. the fan of metal is the person who's sport is basketball##1
 7. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
 8. the spanish is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
10. the russian is in an even position##4
11. the russian is on the far right##1
12. the fan of blues is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | metal      | blues | soul     | country        |
| Nationality   | brazilian | spanish  | mexican     | russian |
| Sport         | basketball    | climbing | surfing      | ice-hockey |
| Transport     | bus | boat     | tram | trike       |

 